name: BTS, Percent Departures On-Time at U.S. Airports, 2005
description: This data reports the percent of flights that departed on time for airports in the U.S. and for the year 2005. The original data comes from monthly numbers "reported by US certified air carriers that account for at least one percent of domestic scheduled passenger revenues--includes scheduled and actual arrival and departure times for flights." www.bts.gov
